data.description: Seize the chance to make this meticulously upgraded 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence your very own. Boasting over 1,500 square feet, this home offers a spacious dining area for enjoyable meals, a kitchen with contemporary flooring, fresh cabinets, sleek countertops, and a convenient walk-in pantry. Additional living spaces include a den/office, a mudroom, a welcoming family room, and a full block basement that provides ample storage options. Not to mention the partially finished basement. The property is enhanced by a newer roof and furnace, along with professional insulation throughout the entire home. There's no need for additional renovations - it's time to move in and relish the comforts of your new abode.
